ivatisation of criminal justice services and questions of legitimacy and governance, this is essential reading for everyone interested in the future of the service.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aCriminalsxRehabilitationzGreat Britain. 0aProbationxGovernment policyzGreat Britain. 0aProbationzGreat Britain. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh1 aFeilzer, Martina, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311119642840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447327295423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447327295/original  a978-3-11-119642-8  Bristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles